<h2>Environmental benefits</h2>
<p>Switching from a traditional pool to a natural ecosystem pond has wide-reaching benefits:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Water Conservation: Less evaporation, no draining for chemical balancing.</li>
    <li>Carbon Footprint Reduction: Minimal energy use compared to electric filters and heaters.</li>
    <li>Pollinator Support: Attracts bees, butterflies, and other beneficial insects.</li>
    <li>Biodiversity: A habitat for amphibians, birds, and aquatic life.</li>
</ul>
